data.title: Maria Zofia Czartoryska
data.meta_description: Countess Maria Zofia Czartoryska née Sieniawska was a Polish szlachcianka (noblewoman). By birth she was member of powerful Sieniawski family and by marriage she was member of House of Dönhoff and House of Czartoryski.
